<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Classroom 6x - Play Ice Cream Catcher Unblocked Online</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f7f6; }
        .game-container { text-align: center; background: #fff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 30px; }
        canvas { background: #1a1a1a; display: block; margin: 10px auto; border-radius: 8px; cursor: crosshair; }
        .article-section { background: #fff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); text-align: left; }
        h1, h2 { color: #2c3e50; }
        .score-board { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #e74c3c; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .backlink { display: inline-block; margin-top: 20px; padding: 10px 20px; background: #3498db; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: bold; }
        .backlink:hover { background: #2980b9; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="game-container">
        <h1>Ice Cream Catcher: Classroom 6x Edition</h1>
        <div class="score-board">Score: <span id="scoreVal">0</span></div>
        <canvas id="gameCanvas" width="400" height="500"></canvas>
        <p>Use your mouse to catch the falling treats!</p>
        <a href="https://classrooms-6x.com/" class="backlink">Play More at Classroom 6x</a>
    </div>

    <div class="article-section">
        <h2>Why Classroom 6x is the Best Choice for Students</h2>
        <p>In today's digital age, finding quality entertainment during breaks can be a challenge. That's where <strong>classroom 6x</strong> comes in. This platform provides a safe and fun environment for students to enjoy their favorite browser games without any restrictions.</p>
        
        <h3>The Benefits of Browser Gaming</h3>
        <p>Playing simple games like our Ice Cream Catcher on <strong>classroom 6x</strong> helps in improving hand-eye coordination and provides a much-needed mental break. Unlike heavy downloads, these HTML5 games start instantly in any browser.</p>

        <h2>How to Play This Game</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Move your mouse left and right to control the blue paddle.</li>
            <li>Catch the pink ice cream balls to increase your score.</li>
            <li>Try to get the highest score possible before the break ends!</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For more unblocked fun, don't forget to visit the official <strong>classroom 6x</strong> website and explore thousands of free games.</p>
    </div>

    <script>
        const canvas = document.getElementById("gameCanvas");
        const ctx = canvas.getContext("2d");
        let score = 0, playerX = 175, items = [];

        document.addEventListener("mousemove", (e) => {
            let rect = canvas.getBoundingClientRect();
            playerX = e.clientX - rect.left - 35;
            if (playerX < 0) playerX = 0;
            if (playerX > 330) playerX = 330;
        });

        function spawn() { items.push({ x: Math.random() * 370 + 15, y: 0, s: 3 + Math.random() * 2 }); }

        function draw() {
            ctx.clearRect(0, 0, 400, 500);
            ctx.fillStyle = "#3498db";
            ctx.fillRect(playerX, 470, 70, 15);
            items.forEach((it, i) => {
                it.y += it.s;
                ctx.fillStyle = "#ff7675";
                ctx.beginPath();
                ctx.arc(it.x, it.y, 12, 0, Math.PI * 2);
                ctx.fill();
                if (it.y > 470 && it.x > playerX && it.x < playerX + 70) {
                    score++;
                    document.getElementById("scoreVal").innerText = score;
                    items.splice(i, 1);
                } else if (it.y > 500) { items.splice(i, 1); }
            });
            requestAnimationFrame(draw);
        }
        setInterval(spawn, 800);
        draw();
    </script>
</body>
</html>
